   186	- ✓ POST `/records` with `{"record_date": "2026-04-14"}` → 201, DB `Record.date == 2026-04-14`
   187	- ✓ POST `/records` without record_date → 201, DB `Record.date == today`
   188	- ✓ POST `/records` with `{"record_date": null}` → 201, DB `Record.date == today`
   189	- ✗ POST `/records` with old `{"date": "2026-04-14"}` → 被 pydantic 忽略（extra 字段），实际日期走 default today
   190	- 关键行为：班主任补录昨天积分功能真可用
   191	
   192	**边界条件**：
